{"Directions": ["In a salad bowl, combine the greens, onion, grapefruit, mushrooms and water chestnuts. In a small bowl, whisk together the dressing ingredients. Drizzle over salad; serve immediately."], "Image": "http://images.media-allrecipes.com/userphotos/250x250/978140.jpg", "Recipe": "Greens 'n' Grapefruit Salad", "Ingredients": ["4 cups torn salad greens", "2 tablespoons chopped red onion", "1 medium grapefruit, peeled and sectioned", "1/2 cup sliced fresh mushrooms", "1/2 cup sliced water chestnuts", "DRESSING:", "1/2 cup mayonnaise or salad dressing", "1/4 cup Catalina salad dressing", "1/4 cup sesame seeds, toasted", "2 tablespoons sugar", "2 tablespoons cider vinegar"]}